=begin
  gshunting4all.lic
  Universal hunting engine for GemStone IV (Lich 5) with integrated GTK3 setup wizard.
  Saves per-character profiles in gsh4a_profiles/<name>.yaml.

  Author: Falvicar
  Bugs, issues, or suggestions? Reach out to Falvicar in-game or on Discord: Shadowleaves

  Usage:
    ;gshunting4all setup    -- open the setup GUI to create or update your profile
    ;gshunting4all          -- start hunting using your saved profile
    ;gshunting4all stop     -- stop the script

  In game during a hunt:
    PAUSE    -- hold attacks (emergency abilities and society symbols still active)
    RESUME   -- resume attacks

  IMPORTANT -- This script is NOT an AFK or room-travel script:
    Movement between rooms is intentionally left to the player. This script handles
    combat only -- activating abilities, tracking cooldowns, managing techniques,
    and keeping you safe while you hunt. It exists to improve quality of life given
    how many items and abilities now require manual activation mid-combat. You still
    move, you still make decisions. The script handles the rest so you can stay
    focused on the game.

  Setup note:
    When you run ;gshunting4all setup, the wizard automatically detects your equipped
    gear, known spells, society, arcarium, gemstones, and combat item scripts. This
    detection process runs at launch and takes roughly a minute to complete -- this is
    normal. Make sure you are fully equipped before running setup so everything is
    detected correctly.
    The setup wizard only shows options relevant to your profession and equipped gear.
    A Warrior will not see Bard sonic options; a Bard will not see Paladin spell options.
    What you see is what applies to you.

  Group hunting:
    The script supports grouped play. It will hold attacks if a non-grouped player
    enters the room before combat begins (anti-poaching). If you are grouped with
    other players, their presence will not interrupt combat.
    Note: eloot runs after each kill by default. If you are grouped and do not want
    the script looting, uncheck "Use eloot" in Hunting Preferences during setup.

  Combat systems supported:
    - Weapons: primary, secondary, dual wield, UAC, ambush/hide
    - Bard sonic: weapon, shield, armor (Songs tab)
    - Mount: summon, charge (stance offensive auto-set), trample
    - Spells: maintained buffs, single-target rotation, AoE rotation
    - Paladin spells: 1635 Divine Intervention (BESEECH, opt-in), 1650 Divine Incarnation
      (INCARNATE ARMOR/ZEAL/SMITE/ONSLAUGHT, opt-in per ability)
    - CMANs and Weapon Techniques (assault/reaction/aoe) with cooldown tracking
    - Shield specs and Armor specs
    - Societies: Voln, Council of Light, Sunfist -- maintain buffs + on-demand symbols
    - Arcarium: Aversaris and Vangaris vissi (per-ability when/cooldown/daily limit)
    - Combat item scripts (auto-detected): Valence, Duskbringer, Celestial Fury,
      Icestrike Lance, Runebow, Nerve Staff, Spectral Dagger, Tempest Blade,
      Elemental Runestaff, Shadow Gauntlet, Nightshade Crossbow, Resonant Runestone,
      Misenseor Badge, Festive Confetti Bow, Ensorcelled/Unholy/Veil Iron weapon,
      Aelotoi's Breath, Zareen's Lullaby, Blade of Mirrors, Arcanist's Rune,
      Sigil Set (Sigil Staff, Mana-Infused Armor, Dramatic Drapery), and more
    - Trinkets: Energy Wings Pin, Battle Standard, Elemental Gloves, Twisted Gloves,
      Twisted Kicks, Mage's Gauntlet, Magic Gloves, Mana Battery Jewelry
    - Gemstones: up to 5 slots with activated ability/when/cooldown tracking
    - Eloot integration (auto-loot after kills, disable in Hunting Preferences if grouped)

  Safety features:
    - Health retreat: immediate retreat (go2, Symbol of Return, or stop) at threshold
    - Encumbrance watcher: background thread retreats at configurable encumbrance level
    - Town/friendly NPC protection: hardcoded blocklist (guards, constables, sheriffs,
      marshals, etc.) + user-configurable Never Attack list; checked before every attack
    - Gigas peace: optional checkbox to never attack gigas and suppress all AoE/multi
      abilities while any gigas are present in the room (Hinterwilds)
    - Anti-poaching: holds attacks if a non-grouped player is in the room before
      combat starts; ignores players who arrive mid-fight (you were there first)
    - Dead player detection: auto-pauses if a dead player is in the room
    - Stale script detection: saved items not detected at setup shown with orange
      warning and Remove button

  Cooldown tracking:
    - All abilities (scripts, trinkets, gemstones, arcarium, CMANs, techniques,
      mount charge/trample) are tracked internally and not re-fired while on CD
    - Weapon techniques additionally watched via downstream hook for game CD messages
    - fput_guarded safety net catches game rejection responses for item abilities
=end

require 'yaml'
require 'fileutils'

PROFILE_DIR = File.join(File.dirname(__FILE__), "gsh4a_profiles")
FileUtils.mkdir_p(PROFILE_DIR)

CASTER_NOUNS = %w[
  conjurer mage wizard necromancer shaman priest sorcerer warlock
  channeler ritualist arcanist scholar sage invoker summoner adept
].freeze

# Nouns/names that must never be attacked -- town authority and non-hostile NPCs.
# Checked against both NPC noun and full name so partial matches (e.g. "town guard") are caught.
GIGAS_PATTERN = /\bgigas\b/i.freeze

SAFE_NPC_PATTERN = /\b(
  guard|constable|sheriff|marshal|marshall|deputy|watchman|watch|
  militia|militiaman|bailiff|magistrate|judge|warden|enforcer|
  captain|lieutenant|sergeant|corporal|officer|soldier|sentinel|
  alderman|councilor|chancellor|steward|herald|emissary|envoy|
  banker|clerk|shopkeeper|merchant|vendor|innkeeper|bartender|
  healer|herbalist|townsfolk|citizen|commoner|peasant|beggar|
  child|infant|baby|youth|elder|grandmother|grandfather
)\b/xi.freeze

VOLN_SYMBOL_BUFFS = {
  "symbol of blessing"      => "Symbol of Blessing",
  "symbol of protection"    => "Symbol of Protection",
  "symbol of courage"       => "Symbol of Courage",
  "symbol of supremacy"     => "Symbol of Supremacy",
  "symbol of retribution"   => "Symbol of Retribution",
  "symbol of transcendence" => "Symbol of Transcendence",
  "symbol of disruption"    => "Symbol of Disruption",
}.freeze

REJECT_PATTERN = /recently|cannot|not yet|too soon|does not respond|no effect|still in cooldown|already used/i

